### Add spanners

Table spanners can be added quickly with `tab_spanner()` and again use either position (column number) or + `vars(name)`.

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
yield_data_wide %>% 
  head() %>%
  gt(
    groupname_col = "crop",
    rowname_col = "Country"
  ) %>% 
  tab_spanner(
    label = "Yield in Tonnes/Hectare", 
    columns = 2:5
    )
```

